      "text": [
        "173 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «غُسْلُ اَلْجَنَابَةِ وَ اَلْحَيْضِ وَاحِدٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.173 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n'The ghusl (ritual bath) for janabah (ritual impurity due to sexual discharge) and menstruation is the same.'."
        ]
      }
    }
